# Vercel API routes and crons

Read **CLAUDE.md** server path and **agents.md** analytics/subscriptions section.

## Server-only

Use supabase-admin and server env vars (service role, SMTP, Razorpay secrets, internal API secret). Never import admin client in pages or components.

## Crons

Scheduled jobs are declared in vercel.json — keepalive (Supabase idle prevention), subscription daily digest, auto-deliver slots. Match route paths when adding new crons.

## Patterns

Follow existing route structure: typed Vercel handler, admin client for DB, user-friendly errors, log failures. Email is best-effort where already documented.

New env vars: add to .env.example with a short comment; never commit secrets.
